{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redstone Realty</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #A00000;\n            --secondary-color: #E0E0E0;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background: #f4f4f4;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/A00000/FFFFFF?text=Elegant+Homes') center/cover no-repeat;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 8px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero h3 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .property-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .property-card {\n            background: var(--light-text-color);\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .property-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .property-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .property-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .property-info h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .property-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .property-info .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #700000;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Redstone Realty</h1>\n            <p>Crafting dreams, building futures.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#properties\">Properties</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Discover Your Perfect Home</h3>\n            <p>Timeless elegance, modern living.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"properties\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n        <div class=\"property-grid\">\n            <div class=\"property-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/CCCCCC/000000?text=Modern+Villa\" alt=\"Modern Villa\">\n                <div class=\"property-info\">\n                    <h4>Stunning Modern Villa</h4>\n                    <p>5 Beds | 4 Baths | 4000 sqft</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$1,500,000</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"property-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/CCCCCC/000000?text=Charming+Apartment\" alt=\"Charming Apartment\">\n                <div class=\"property-info\">\n                    <h4>Charming City Apartment</h4>\n                    <p>2 Beds | 2 Baths | 1200 sqft</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$650,000</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"property-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/CCCCCC/000000?text=Spacious+Townhouse\" alt=\"Spacious Townhouse\">\n                <div class=\"property-info\">\n                    <h4>Spacious Family Townhouse</h4>\n                    <p>3 Beds | 3 Baths | 2200 sqft</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$875,000</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p>Redstone Realty is more than just a brokerage; we are curators of sophisticated living spaces. With a passion for art and architecture, we handpick properties that resonate with elegance, comfort, and timeless design. Our dedicated team is committed to providing an unparalleled real estate experience, guiding you with integrity and expertise from search to sale.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n            <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n            <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n            <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n            <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Redstone Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic interactivity if needed in the future\n        document.querySelector('button[type=\"submit\"]').addEventListener('click', function() {\n            alert('Message sent! We will be in touch shortly.');\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}